            <description><![CDATA[好耶是我爱的鸭血粉丝汤 <br> <br>【39.9】南京冠生园 鸭血粉丝汤168g*4盒 <br> <br>平时线下都要十几二十块一碗了现在只要10大洋就能到手！吃起来味道很香浓也没有什么鸭腥味👌鸭血嫩嫩的鸭肠脆脆的每一口都好吃到不行 <br> <br>还可以往里面放点豆泡青菜之类的进去吸汁也好好吃哦！特别是汤底浓浓的鲜香，好吃到汤都要喝光<img style="" src="https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h5amku3ymrj20j60j6q5q.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h5amkuykkcj20j60j6mze.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h5amkvrroxj20gn0ihtaj.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h5amkwmu1gj20j60p4wgf.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h5amkxgy2rj20fv0iy3zp.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h5amkyaitwj20j60pjwh9.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
